{
  "stem": "3631.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, Goth ordered that some-- some masons-- they had to-- to close up his door to Johann's villa-- a little house that he had.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put more bricks in and close it up so that he couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Crazy things and funny things happened, too, once in a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During this period of time, were you aware of any observances of religious life in Plaszow?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of any-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Pla-- Well, in Krakow, where we were in-- in Krakow, or in Plaszow?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Plaszow-- I was not aware, but there was no official, organized Jewish life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Orthodox Jews, I'm sure, kept their morning prayer and their evening prayer, and they kept on the holidays they try to keep some sort of-- some sort of--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were still some synagogues-- some temples in operation where we were-- where we were [INAUDIBLE] I think in the ghetto, I think there was one or two.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They may have met informally to-- to pray.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The High Holidays, I think, were in an informal way observed as well-- as well as could be done.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I told you that incident with my mother, with her teeth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was definitely an act of kindness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Offhand, I could not think of any, really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There-- there was food smuggled into the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think I remember reading something that some money was smuggled in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we knew the Wasserbergers-- that family had a very responsible men in their mill who sometimes bought us food into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think  he brought some money in to be distributed among others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think that was done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The details, I do not remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am not aware of any.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
